nodes.text: The desert moon of Oba Diah, also known simply as the Oba Diah moon, was a desert moon that orbited the planet Oba Diah, located near Kessel in the galaxy's Outer Rim Territories. Prior to the Clone Wars, a T-6 shuttle belonging to Jedi Master Sifo-Dyas was shot down to crash on the moon, and circa 20 BBY, the clone troopers of Wolfpack found the remnants of the shuttle on the moon.
